71  struct EDMA_TCD_STD_tag { /* for "standard" format TCDs (when EDMA.TCD[x].CITER.E_LINK==BITER.E_LINK=0 && EDMA.EMLM=0 ) */
72  /* 00 */
73  vuint32_t SADDR; /* Source Address */
74 
75  /* 04 */ /* Transfer Attributes */
76  vuint16_t SMOD:5; /* Source Address Modulo */
77  vuint16_t SSIZE:3; /* Source Data Transfer Size */
78  vuint16_t DMOD:5; /* Destination Address Modulo */
79  vuint16_t DSIZE:3; /* Destination Data Transfer Size */
80 
81  /* 06 */
82  vint16_t SOFF; /* Signed Source Address Offset */
83 
84  /* 08 */
85  vuint32_t NBYTES; /* Inner ("Minor") Byte Transfer Count */
86 
87  /* 0C */
88  vint32_t SLAST; /* Last Source Address Adjustment */
89 
90  /* 10 */
91  vuint32_t DADDR; /* Destination Address */
92 
93  /* 14 */
94  vuint16_t CITERE_LINK:1; /* Enable Channel-to-Channel */
95  /* Linking on Minor Loop Completion */
96  vuint16_t CITER:15; /* Current Major Iteration Count */
97 
98  /* 16 */
99  vint16_t DOFF; /* Signed Destination Address Offset */
100 
101  /* 18 */
102  vint32_t DLAST_SGA; /* Last Destination Address Adjustment, or */
103  /* Scatter/Gather Address (if E_SG = 1) */
104 
105  /* 1C */
106  vuint16_t BITERE_LINK:1; /* Enable Channel-to-Channel */
107  /* Linking on Minor Loop Complete */
108  vuint16_t BITER:15; /* Starting ("Major") Iteration Count */
109 
110  /* 1E */ /* Channel Control/Status */
111  vuint16_t BWC:2; /* Bandwidth Control */
112  vuint16_t MAJORLINKCH:6; /* Link Channel Number */
113  vuint16_t DONE:1; /* Channel Done */
114  vuint16_t ACTIVE:1;
115  vuint16_t MAJORE_LINK:1; /* Enable Channel-to-Channel Link */
116  vuint16_t E_SG:1; /* Enable Scatter/Gather Descriptor */
117  vuint16_t D_REQ:1; /* Disable IPD_REQ When Done */
118  vuint16_t INT_HALF:1; /* Interrupt on CITER = (BITER >> 1) */
119  vuint16_t INT_MAJ:1; /* Interrupt on Major Loop Completion */
120  vuint16_t START:1; /* Explicit Channel Start */
121  };
